Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.13,0:59:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 哈里谢顿生命机能已停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Designate Hari Seldon's life functions have ceased.
